-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="sc-59baed0b-4 hfpWCv">Save</span></div><p class="sc-59baed0b-0 sc-59baed0b-3 fuyVND cAOLoR">essay</p><p class="sc-59baed0b-0 sc-59baed0b-2 fuyVND ePEXnI">Music</p></div><p class="sc-59baed0b-10 gqsGJu">A novel kind of music</p><p class="sc-59baed0b-11 llxLtL">So-called ‘classical’ music was as revolutionary as the modern novel in its storytelling, harmony and depth</p><p class="sc-59baed0b-0 sc-59baed0b-12 fuyVND cWJVNA">Joel Sandelson</p></div><div class="sc-59baed0b-6 dtyrwz"></div></div></a><a href="/essays/how-psychology-can-be-a-tool-for-postcolonial-freedom"><div class="sc-59baed0b-9 koxOCA"><div type="essay" class="sc-4c9ef492-2 kQFYIz"><img alt="A black-and-white photo of soldiers in uniform checking documents of several men standing outdoors, with laundry hanging in the background." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/d399ecd9-a857-4d37-a45a-0912658a3871/essay-final-par53942.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/d399ecd9-a857-4d37-a45a-0912658a3871/essay-final-par53942.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/d399ecd9-a857-4d37-a45a-0912658a3871/essay-final-par53942.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/d399ecd9-a857-4d37-a45a-0912658a3871/essay-final-par53942.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/d399ecd9-a857-4d37-a45a-0912658a3871/essay-final-par53942.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/d399ecd9-a857-4d37-a45a-0912658a3871/essay-final-par53942.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/d399ecd9-a857-4d37-a45a-0912658a3871/essay-final-par53942.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/d399ecd9-a857-4d37-a45a-0912658a3871/essay-final-par53942.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/d399ecd9-a857-4d37-a45a-0912658a3871/essay-final-par53942.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/d399ecd9-a857-4d37-a45a-0912658a3871/essay-final-par53942.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 3840w" src="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/d399ecd9-a857-4d37-a45a-0912658a3871/essay-final-par53942.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto"/></div><div class="sc-59baed0b-1 HnFfS"><div class="sc-59baed0b-8 bIyzxX"><div class="sc-59baed0b-5 bgoMLi"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="sc-59baed0b-4 hfpWCv">Save</span></div><p class="sc-59baed0b-0 sc-59baed0b-3 fuyVND cAOLoR">essay</p><p class="sc-59baed0b-0 sc-59baed0b-2 fuyVND ePEXnI">Psychiatry and psychotherapy</p></div><p class="sc-59baed0b-10 gqsGJu">Decolonising psychology</p><p class="sc-59baed0b-11 llxLtL">At times complicit in racism and oppression, psychology has also been a fertile ground for radical and liberatory thought</p><p class="sc-59baed0b-0 sc-59baed0b-12 fuyVND cWJVNA">Rami Gabriel</p></div><div class="sc-59baed0b-6 dtyrwz"></div></div></a></div></div></div></div><footer class="sc-c1f448ad-0 cpbdkK footer"><div class="sc-ae266dcd-0 sc-c1f448ad-1 bwTVbW gnOaXO"><div class="sc-1b596d24-0 ithRRD"><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/essays" class="sc-11b024c5-0 fQckeD">Essays</a><a href="/ideas" class="sc-1